WEBVTT

00:01.521 --> 00:04.015
Hey baby girl, let's talk about boys.

00:04.617 --> 00:07.276
You're going to hate them, and then you're going to love them.

00:08.250 --> 00:09.399
Your heart will be broken.

00:10.005 --> 00:12.932
But one day, you'll find someone who loves you almost as much as I do.

00:13.821 --> 00:16.145
Don't worry too much about what other people think of you, okay?

00:17.200 --> 00:19.265
And don't ever worry about not being good enough.

00:19.820 --> 00:20.775
You're perfect.

00:28.181 --> 00:30.072
Now, about shoes.

